folder: Moffat Street & Knickerbocker Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Moffat Street, north of Knickerbocker Ave., showing in the background the mansion of J.E. Van Nostrand, which was demolished in April 1929. This is a set of 2 views showing same in Queens County at Wyckoff and Cooper Aves.

November 1923.
View 2:-January 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
